704738f-b.text:
Halsey Street (trolley cars thereon), north of Irving Ave. (about 300 feet) to Wyckoff Ave. This is a set of two views. View No. 2 shows sections of QQueens Co., beyond the B.M.T. Elevated Line on Wyckoff Ave. In the foreground of the same view is seen a Long Island
Rtailroad crossing.
October 1928.
View 2:eFebruary 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Gollection.
